{"id":219576,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2012/04/global-voices-缅甸：透过脸书监控选举/","date":"2012-04-06T13:46:39Z","modified":"2012-04-06T13:46:39Z","title":"Global Voices | 缅甸：透过脸书监控选举","content":"<p><p>缅甸在过去几年已经实施许多改革，包括<a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"http://globalvoicesonline.org/2011/11/01/myanmar-a-year-after-suu-kyis-release/\" href=\"http://globalvoicesonline.org/2011/11/01/myanmar-a-year-after-suu-kyis-release/\">释放</a>民主运动领袖翁山苏姬、暂缓争议性的<a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"http://globalvoicesonline.org/2011/10/05/myanmar-president-suspends-dam-project/\" href=\"http://globalvoicesonline.org/2011/10/05/myanmar-president-suspends-dam-project/\">水坝</a>兴建计划，并前所未有地释放上百位政治犯。如今，是选举的时候了。</p>\n<p>两大主要政党─翁山苏姬领导的全国民主联盟，以及前任军事将领主导的联邦巩固与发展党，正在竞争国会的48个席次，其他小党像是民主党、新全国民主党、民主联邦党…等政党，则在竞争其他少数的席次。</p>\n<p>选举刚好选在愚人节这天，缅甸的脸书使用者也被不同新闻浪潮包围。</p>\n<p>Khin Nyein Chan<a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"https://www.facebook.com/photo.php?fbid=3215726165989&#038;set=a.2450847284495.121076.1651390024&#038;type=1\" href=\"https://www.facebook.com/photo.php?fbid=3215726165989&#038;set=a.2450847284495.121076.1651390024&#038;type=1\">发布</a>一张联邦巩固与发展党的竞选照片，这张照片是在美国国务卿希拉蕊去年十一月拜访缅甸时所拍的。许多脸书使用者评论，这样竞选方式十分不恰当：</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>狮子想高飞威胁孔雀<br />却飞不起来而跌倒</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>Mg Mg Lwin Eu<a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"https://www.facebook.com/photo.php?fbid=406478166033879&#038;set=a.173177339363964.49625.100000150984325&#038;type=1&#038;theater\" href=\"https://www.facebook.com/photo.php?fbid=406478166033879&#038;set=a.173177339363964.49625.100000150984325&#038;type=1&#038;theater\">写道</a>，相较于全国民主联盟十分成功的竞选活动，<a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"https://www.facebook.com/demowaiyen\" href=\"https://www.facebook.com/demowaiyen\">Demo Waiyan</a>所发布联邦巩固与发展党竞选<a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"https://www.facebook.com/photo.php?fbid=406478166033879&#038;set=a.173177339363964.49625.100000150984325&#038;type=1&#038;theater\" href=\"https://www.facebook.com/photo.php?fbid=406478166033879&#038;set=a.173177339363964.49625.100000150984325&#038;type=1&#038;theater\">照片</a>，就像很多人被迫要参加一场演讲一样。</p>\n<p> </p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.facebook.com/photo.php?fbid=409241702424192&#038;set=a.173177339363964.49625.100000150984325&#038;type=1\"><img title=\"election campaign\" src=\"http://globalvoicesonline.org/wp-content/uploads/2012/04/election-campaign-375x250.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"375\" height=\"250\" /></a></p>\n<p>缅甸选举</p>\n</div>\n<p>同时，也有来源未知的新闻报导和谣言，具有极大冲击，并可能影响选举结果。Demo Waiyan<a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"https://www.facebook.com/photo.php?fbid=409241702424192&#038;set=a.173177339363964.49625.100000150984325&#038;type=1\" href=\"https://www.facebook.com/photo.php?fbid=409241702424192&#038;set=a.173177339363964.49625.100000150984325&#038;type=1\">分享</a>一则他听到的新闻，这则新闻说，选票的空白勾选处，某些地方已经上了蜡，让选民可能无法顺利投票。</p>\n<p>某些据信真的发生的谣言，听起来像是愚人节的恶作剧。其中一则<a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"https://www.facebook.com/demo.fatty/posts/10150652221521374\" href=\"https://www.facebook.com/demo.fatty/posts/10150652221521374\">宣称</a>：联邦巩固与发展党企图把一件衬衫和帽子 给曼德勒的一名乞丐，但这乞丐拒绝接受这些礼物。某些人<a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"https://www.facebook.com/demo.fatty/posts/10150650407256374\" href=\"https://www.facebook.com/demo.fatty/posts/10150650407256374\">说</a>，联邦巩固与发展党在曼德勒的Tadar Oo整夜一直用声音极大的喇叭羞辱全国民主联盟。最近，有关联邦巩固与发展党的<a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"https://www.facebook.com/notes/burma-vj-media-network/%E1%80%92%E1%80%B6%E1%80%B1%E1%80%95%E1%80%AB%E1%80%80%E1%80%B9%E1%80%B1%E1%80%80%E1%80%BC%E1%80%BA%E1%80%B8%E1%81%BF%E1%80%95%E1%80%AE%E1%80%B8-%E1%80%98%E1%80%AF%E1%80%9B%E1%80%AC%E1%80%B8%E1%80%96%E1%80%B0%E1%80%B8%E1%80%95%E1%80%AF%E1%80%AD%E1%82%94%E1%80%B1%E1%80%95%E1%80%B8%E1%80%99%E1%80%8A%E1%80%B9%E1%80%B7-%E1%82%80%E1%80%80%E1%80%B6%E1%82%95%E1%80%96%E1%80%BC%E1%80%B6%E1%82%94/375088979179876\" href=\"https://www.facebook.com/notes/burma-vj-media-network/%E1%80%92%E1%80%B6%E1%80%B1%E1%80%95%E1%80%AB%E1%80%80%E1%80%B9%E1%80%B1%E1%80%80%E1%80%BC%E1%80%BA%E1%80%B8%E1%81%BF%E1%80%95%E1%80%AE%E1%80%B8-%E1%80%98%E1%80%AF%E1%80%9B%E1%80%AC%E1%80%B8%E1%80%96%E1%80%B0%E1%80%B8%E1%80%95%E1%80%AF%E1%80%AD%E1%82%94%E1%80%B1%E1%80%95%E1%80%B8%E1%80%99%E1%80%8A%E1%80%B9%E1%80%B7-%E1%82%80%E1%80%80%E1%80%B6%E1%82%95%E1%80%96%E1%80%BC%E1%80%B6%E1%82%94/375088979179876\">最有名的谣言</a>，就是他们在仰光的East Dagon镇送印度香饭给民众，当做他们的竞选策略。也有人<a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"https://www.facebook.com/photo.php?fbid=10150642319061374&#038;set=p.10150642319061374&#038;type=1提及\" href=\"https://www.facebook.com/photo.php?fbid=10150642319061374&#038;set=p.10150642319061374&#038;type=1%E6%8F%90%E5%8F%8A\">1</a>，联邦巩固与发展党的代表在他的竞选演讲过程中发钞票。</p>\n<p>尽管这是联邦巩固与发展党尽的最大努力，多数人正迫切地支持全国民主联盟，即使并不是他们的所有成员都有资格参加议会补选。在脸书上的一项小<a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"https://www.facebook.com/questions/333298793386283/\" href=\"https://www.facebook.com/questions/333298793386283/\">调查</a>显示，974人说他们会投全国民主联盟，只有24人会投联邦巩固与发展党。</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>我们明天早上五点会去投全国民主联盟</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>这是Myint Mying Khin Pe在脸书上<a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"https://www.facebook.com/ShweZeeKwet/posts/3675437287041\" href=\"https://www.facebook.com/ShweZeeKwet/posts/3675437287041\">发</a>的文，她是演员<a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"https://www.facebook.com/ActorKyawThu/info\" href=\"https://www.facebook.com/ActorKyawThu/info\">Kyaw Thu</a>的妻子，也是自由葬仪服务社群的创立者。</p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.facebook.com/photo.php?fbid=406478166033879&#038;set=a.173177339363964.49625.100000150984325&#038;type=1&#038;theater\"><img title=\"election rally\" src=\"http://globalvoicesonline.org/wp-content/uploads/2012/04/election-rally-375x239.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"375\" height=\"239\" /></a></p>\n<p>USDP竞选活动</p>\n</div>\n<p>Htoo Tay Zar，一名博客和公民媒体记者，写下他对全国民主联盟和联邦巩固与发展党的<a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"https://www.facebook.com/htootayzar/posts/10150709598143913\" href=\"https://www.facebook.com/htootayzar/posts/10150709598143913\">看法</a>：</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>大多数人总是说全国民主联盟是反对党…对我来说，联邦巩固与发展党更像是反对党…今天，我刚好见证了联邦巩固与发展党在Khawmu镇的巡回宣传行程…没人注意他们…他们也并不活跃…党员像是在卡车上睡着…总之，他们是反对党，而且他们反对人们的欲求…=)</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>缅甸的活跃脸书使用者已经表达他们对全国民主联盟和翁山苏姬的支持。翁山苏姬已经抵达Kawt Hmu，她希望在那成为全国民主联盟的议会代表。DVB发布了一则<a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"https://www.facebook.com/photo.php?v=303490709717586\" href=\"https://www.facebook.com/photo.php?v=303490709717586\">影片</a>，是有关翁山苏姬抵达Kawt Hmu，许多人对她胜选有高度期待。也有许多人在脸书上写下“祝缅甸好运”的评论。</p>\n<p>校对：<a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"使用者:Portnoy\" href=\"http://proj.daodin.net/mediawiki/index.php/%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%E8%80E7%BC%85%E7%94%B8%EF%BC%9A%E9%80%8F%E8%BF%87%E8%84%B8%E4%B9%A6%E7%9B%91%E6%8E%A7%E9%80%89%E4%B8%BE&#038;url=http%3A%2F%2Fzh.globalvoicesonline.org%2Fhans%2F2012%2F04%2F06%2F10753%2F&#038;description=&#038;via=sticker\" title=\"HEMiDEMi\"><span>HEMiDEMi</span></a> · <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://myshare.url.com.tw/index.php?func=newurl&#038;url=http%3A%2F%2Fzh.globalvoicesonline.org%2Fhans%2F2012%2F04%2F06%2F10753%2F&#038;desc=%E7%BC%85%E7%94%B8%EF%BC%9A%E9%80%8F%E8%BF%87%E8%84%B8%E4%B9%A6%E7%9B%91%E6%8E%A7%E9%80%89%E4%B8%BE\" title=\"MyShare\"><span>MyShare</span></a> · <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.shouker.com/%22%20onclick=20js=document.createElement%20(\" title=\"Shouker\"><span>Shouker</span></a> · <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.facebook.com/share.php?u=http%3A%2F%2Fzh.globalvoicesonline.org%2Fhans%2F2012%2F04%2F06%2F10753%2F\" title=\"facebook\"><span>facebook</span></a> · <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://twitter.com/share?url=http%3A%2F%2Fzh.globalvoicesonline.org%2Fhans%2F2012%2F04%2F06%2F10753%2F&#038;text=%E7%BC%85%E7%94%B8%EF%BC%9A%E9%80%8F%E8%BF%87%E8%84%B8%E4%B9%A6%E7%9B%91%E6%8E%A7%E9%80%89%E4%B8%BE&#038;via=globalvoiceszh\" title=\"twitter\"><span>twitter</span></a> · <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://reddit.com/submit?url=http%3A%2F%2Fzh.globalvoicesonline.org%2Fhans%2F2012%2F04%2F06%2F10753%2F&#038;title=%E7%BC%85%E7%94%B8%EF%BC%9A%E9%80%8F%E8%BF%87%E8%84%B8%E4%B9%A6%E7%9B%91%E6%8E%A7%E9%80%89%E4%B8%BE\" title=\"reddit\"><span>reddit</span></a> · <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.stumbleupon.com/submit?url=http%3A%2F%2Fzh.globalvoicesonline.